In a wildly unregulated market,

3
00:00:07,050 --> 00:00:11,340
there has been a proliferation of unauthorized NFT art.

4
00:00:11,850 --> 00:00:14,970
These range from people pretending to be an artist,

5
00:00:15,270 --> 00:00:20,160
to metaverse designers making big brand products without licensing.

6
